25
00:01:41,230 --> 00:01:42,350
There must be a mystery behind it.

26
00:01:57,460 --> 00:01:58,260
[Thousand Gold Formula]

27
00:01:58,540 --> 00:02:00,660
[Orchid, bluish-purple.]

28
