[After being ground and dried, it could
be made into a hallucination trigger.]

29
00:02:44,280 --> 00:02:46,430
Weren't you unwell?

30
00:02:47,310 --> 00:02:48,310
I have a headache.

31
00:02:48,630 --> 00:02:50,590
I'm here to find a cure for my headache.

32
00:02:50,870 --> 00:02:52,080
This is Niyue's pharmacy

33
00:02:53,190 --> 00:02:54,520
and book.

34
00:02:54,520 --> 00:02:57,080
Taking without asking
is considered stealing.

35
00:03:03,120 --> 00:03:04,310
This is my own business.

36
00:03:04,310 --> 00:03:05,560
I'll explain it to her.

37
00:03:05,910 --> 00:03:07,240
I don't think you are sick.

38
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:09,400
I think you are feeling guilty.

39
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:11,520
You are the one frowning
when you see me.

40
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:13,470
Are you conscience-stricken?

41
00:03:13,470 --> 00:03:15,680
That's because I get upset
whenever I see you.

42
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:17,560
You are also an eyesore to me.

43
00:03:23,060 --> 00:03:24,100
[Thousand Gold Formula]

44
00:03:25,740 --> 00:03:26,800
[Orchid, bluish-purple.]

45
00:03:26,800 --> 00:03:28,100
[After being ground and dried, it could
be made into a hallucination trigger.]

46
00:03:41,870 --> 00:03:43,710
He actually burned the book.

47
00:03:44,840 --> 00:03:46,630
Is he hiding a secret?

48
00:03:49,590 --> 00:03:50,400
I can't let it go.

49
00:03:51,080 --> 00:03:52,630
I have to think of a way

50
00:03:53,190 --> 00:03:54,310
to try this incense.

51
00:05:12,500 --> 00:05:15,420
♪The lush and fragrant grass
made longing hard to endure♪

52
00:05:15,830 --> 00:05:16,310
Get out.

53
00:05:19,060 --> 00:05:21,900
♪This love is hard to fade away
as it twists and turns endlessly♪

54
00:05:24,630 --> 00:05:26,480
I smelled the fragrance of this incense
during the birthday banquet.

55
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:27,830
Then my father committed suicide.

56
00:05:28,630 --> 00:05:30,630
He and I both smelled
the fragrance just now,

57
00:05:30,630 --> 00:05:32,720
but nothing unusual happened to us.

58
00:05:33,310 --> 00:05:34,630
Maybe my father's death

59
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:36,070
has nothing to do with the incense?

60
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:37,920
But even so,

61
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:39,430
why did he hide the incense

62
00:05:39,430 --> 00:05:40,480
in a secret place?

63
00:05:40,950 --> 00:05:43,000
And why did he burn that book secretly?

64
00:05:43,800 --> 00:05:46,070
Dry these herbs and
grind them into powder.

65
00:05:46,920 --> 00:05:48,720
A sachet made from these herbs

66
00:05:48,720 --> 00:05:50,510
can cool the body, relieve pain,
and is a cure for colds.

67
00:05:50,950 --> 00:05:52,600
This is my exclusive secret recipe.

68
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:53,830
Ling has always liked it.

69
00:05:54,560 --> 00:05:55,360
Yes.

70
00:05:58,920 --> 00:05:59,720
Yes.

71
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:02,430
Maybe the incense was made
specially for him by Niyue.

72
00:06:02,430 --> 00:06:03,600
It's unique.

73
00:06:03,870 --> 00:06:05,680
That's why he cherishes it so much.

74
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:12,720
Mr. Zhao, leads are lost.

75
00:06:13,120 --> 00:06:14,430
There is no evidence

76
00:06:14,430 --> 00:06:16,480
connecting Ling Xiao
and my father's death.

77
00:06:24,100 --> 00:06:26,260
[Bianque Hall]

78
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:39,920
What's going on?

79
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:40,510
What's going on here?

80
00:06:40,510 --> 00:06:42,000
Canglong City has always
had good weather and fortune.

81
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:43,630
When did this kind of thing ever happen?

82
00:06:43,920 --> 00:06:45,800
It's a disaster from heaven!

83
00:06:45,800 --> 00:06:47,430
No one can escape this!

84
00:06:47,680 --> 00:06:50,310
It's a disaster from heaven!

85
00:06:50,830 --> 00:06:51,430
City Lord.

86
00:06:51,430 --> 00:06:53,190
There are already rumors going around

87
00:06:53,190 --> 00:06:54,040
saying that it's divine punishment.

88
00:06:54,190 --> 00:06:55,560
What should we do about this?

89
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:56,720
I don't believe in any kind
of divine punishment.

90
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:57,920
Hanfeng,

91
00:06:58,070 --> 00:07:00,000
send someone quickly to trace
the source.

92
00:07:00,870 --> 00:07:02,950
Then send the shadow guards to build
a shelter in the mansion.

93
00:07:03,240 --> 00:07:04,270
Move all of the sick

94
00:07:04,270 --> 00:07:05,190
to the shelter,

95
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:06,630
and summon the physicians

96
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:07,920
to discuss a strategy.

97
00:07:08,310 --> 00:07:09,920
We must prevent the contagion

98
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:10,950
and appease the residents.

99
00:07:11,270 --> 00:07:12,000
Yes.

100
00:07:20,950 --> 00:07:23,000
You broke

101
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:25,310
this pinwheel of blessing.

102
00:07:30,070 --> 00:07:31,390
You should rely on your own strength

103
00:07:31,750 --> 00:07:33,190
instead of these things.

104
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:49,680
Remember,

105
00:07:50,070 --> 00:07:51,360
although you are a girl,

106
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:52,750
