107
00:07:53,070 --> 00:07:55,190
You can also rely on yourself
to protect your family.

108
00:07:56,980 --> 00:08:00,580
♪I foolishly think♪

109
00:08:00,660 --> 00:08:04,180
♪Unable to sleep, I was intoxicated
by the fragrance of books♪

110
00:08:04,260 --> 00:08:07,820
♪With you, the fragrance fills
the sky together♪

111
00:08:10,400 --> 00:08:10,920
Come.

112
00:08:35,270 --> 00:08:36,390
Your Lordship, here.

113
00:08:36,390 --> 00:08:37,200
Drink some water.

114
00:08:38,910 --> 00:08:39,630
The people of Canglong City

115
00:08:39,630 --> 00:08:41,080
are truly blessed

116
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:43,120
to have a good Lord like you.

117
00:08:43,630 --> 00:08:44,440
Let's go

118
00:08:44,720 --> 00:08:45,480
and have a look at the apothecary.

119
00:08:45,480 --> 00:08:46,080
Yes.

120
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:08,320
- Your Lordship.
- Your Lordship.

121
