[City Lord's Mansion]

122
00:09:18,030 --> 00:09:18,840
This…

123
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:20,320
Look at the situation of His Lordship,

124
00:09:20,320 --> 00:09:21,720
could it be true as the rumors say?

125
00:09:22,080 --> 00:09:24,030
Could it be a divine disaster?

126
00:09:24,030 --> 00:09:24,790
Stop talking nonsense.

127
00:09:25,360 --> 00:09:27,390
